{"tid":2281762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK獲Bloomberg’s Pop Star Power Rankings肯定登上 11 月份冠軍寶座","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T12:08:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be848de1701060c6f0d4064da383491310ce0c3b","tid":2281762,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"從 6 月底開始以新歌橫掃全球的 BLACKPINK，也在正式發行專輯的一個月後，獲選為 Bloomberg（彭博）本月評選的「最有影響力流行藝人」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBloomberg（彭博）於 11 日公開了 &ldquo;Bloomberg&rsquo;s Pop Star Power Rankings&rdquo;（最有影響力流行藝人）排行榜，BLACKPINK 挟著正規一輯〈THE ALBUM〉所掀起的熱烈迴響，擊敗 Cardi B、Justin Bieber、Drake⋯⋯等在美國呼風喚雨的當紅歌手而拿下冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8491b02b53755ab061fe03f5d140468e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-11/131566-884283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8491b02b53755ab061fe03f5d140468e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-11%2F131566-884283.jpg&h=5c7e411d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於 BLACKPINK 從 6 月開始陸續發行 &ldquo;How You Like That&rdquo;、&rdquo;Ice Cream&rdquo; 和 &ldquo;Lovesick Girls&rdquo; 三支 MV，同時也在 YouTube 上播出實境節目，因此在本月的各項評選指標中，她們便憑著出色的 YouTube 觀看次數成績獲得壓倒性優勢。此外在專輯銷量、Spotify 串流播放次數等方面，BLACKPINK 也都位居前十名內，就此組成將她們推上寶座的力量。<br />\n<br />\n如此一來，BLACKPINK 也成為史上第一組在該榜上拿下冠軍的韓國歌手，再度創造了值得關注的新成就！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a616e5b35455e62ca6d2f67d5701f9f0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-11/131566-884284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a616e5b35455e62ca6d2f67d5701f9f0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-11%2F131566-884284.jpg&h=e0bbb4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"558e99b47110ebaa0a713fa7c5eb612185902b95","tid":2281762,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:59:06.000Z","msg":"mylovessss ！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /